
BHUBANESWAR, JAN. 4. Police today arrested the ``stoneman'', a psychopathic serial killer, who created terror in the South Orissa town of Berhampur.
The killer, identified as Maheshwar Padhi, killed seven persons, by smashing their heads with stone and injuring four others, between May 22 and August 29 last year.
Padhi, 26, is probably the youngest psychopathic serial killer in the country.
- UNI
